==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Weather signal
<hw>Weather signal</hw>. <def>Any signal giving information about the
weather. The system used by the United States Weather Bureau includes
temperature, cold or hot wave, rain or snow, wind direction, storm, and
hurricane signals.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Weather station</ent>⟦br⟧
